<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
<title>Protocol Intelligence - Pievra News</title>
<meta name="description" content="In-depth analysis of every AI agent protocol shaping programmatic advertising in 2025 - AdCP, MCP, UCP/Agentic Audiences, ARTF and A2A. Real launch dates, correct versions, verified facts."/>
<link rel="canonical" href="https://pievra.com/news"/>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<!-- GA4 Analytics - consent-gated (GDPR/CNIL compliant) -->
<script src="/static/consent.js"></script>
<style>
:root{--ink:#18181B;--ink-soft:#52525B;--ink-muted:#71717A;--surface:#FEFDFB;--surface-2:#F9F8F6;--surface-card:#FFFFFF;--accent:#F97316;--accent-hover:#EA580C;--accent-light:#FFF7ED;--accent-border:#FDBA74;--sky:#0EA5E9;--border:#E4E4E7;--border-strong:#D4D4D8;--radius:12px;--radius-lg:20px;--shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(249,115,22,0.06);--shadow-lg:0 12px 48px rgba(249,115,22,0.06)}
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;background:var(--surface);color:var(--ink);line-height:1.7;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
h1{font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;line-height:1.1;font-weight:400}
h2,h3,h4,h5{font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;line-height:1.2}
nav{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;background:var(--surface);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);height:64px;display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 32px;justify-content:space-between}
.nav-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;text-decoration:none}
.logo-mark{display:none}
.logo-text{font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:24px;color:var(--ink)}
.nav-links{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px}
.nav-links a{font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:var(--ink-muted);text-decoration:none;transition:all .2s;padding:8px 14px;border-radius:8px}
.nav-links a:hover,.nav-links a.active{color:var(--ink);background:var(--surface-2)}
.nav-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.btn-ghost{padding:7px 16px;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--ink);background:none;border:1.5px solid var(--border-strong);cursor:pointer;border-radius:8px;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;transition:all .2s}
.btn-ghost:hover{border-color:var(--ink);background:var(--surface-2)}
.btn-primary{padding:7px 18px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:white;background:var(--accent);border:none;cursor:pointer;border-radius:8px;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;transition:all .2s}
.btn-primary:hover{background:var(--accent-hover)}
.news-hero{background:var(--surface);padding:48px 32px 36px;text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.section-tag{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--accent);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px}
.news-hero h1{font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,60px);font-weight:400;font-style:italic;color:var(--ink);letter-spacing:-1px;margin-bottom:16px}
.news-hero p{font-size:17px;color:var(--ink-muted);max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 32px;line-height:1.7}
.news-filters{display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.nf{padding:8px 18px;border-radius:8px;border:1.5px solid var(--border-strong);background:transparent;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;color:var(--ink-muted)}
.nf.active,.nf:hover{background:var(--accent);color:white;border-color:var(--accent)}
.news-layout{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:36px 32px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 300px;gap:40px;align-items:start}
.article-card{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);overflow:hidden;background:var(--surface-card);margin-bottom:32px;transition:all .2s}
.article-card:hover{border-color:var(--accent-border);box-shadow:0 12px 48px rgba(249,115,22,.06)}
.article-header{padding:32px 32px 24px}
.meta-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:16px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.pb{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 12px;border-radius:20px;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase}
.pb-adcp{background:#dbeafe;color:#1d4ed8}
.pb-mcp{background:#d1fae5;color:#065f46}
.pb-ucp{background:#fef3c7;color:#92400e}
.pb-artf{background:#fce7f3;color:#9d174d}
.pb-a2a{background:#ede9fe;color:#5b21b6}
.badge-new{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c3aed,#a855f7);color:white;font-size:10px;font-weight:800;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;letter-spacing:.5px;animation:shim 2.5s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes shim{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.75}}
.art-date{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-muted)}
.article-title{font-size:21px;font-weight:800;color:var(--ink);letter-spacing:-.5px;margin-bottom:10px}
.article-excerpt{font-size:15px;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:12px}
.source-line{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-muted);margin-bottom:18px}
.source-line a{color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none}
.source-line a:hover{text-decoration:underline}
.expand-btn{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--accent);background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;padding:0;transition:gap .2s}
.expand-btn:hover{gap:12px}
.expand-btn .arr{transition:transform .25s;display:inline-block}
.expand-btn.open .arr{transform:rotate(90deg)}
.article-body{display:none;padding:0 32px 32px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.article-body.open{display:block}
.article-body h3{font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);margin:28px 0 10px}
.article-body h3:first-child{margin-top:28px}
.article-body p{font-size:15px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:14px;line-height:1.8}
.article-body ul,.article-body ol{margin:0 0 16px 22px}
.article-body li{font-size:15px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:7px;line-height:1.6}
.article-body strong{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600}
.article-body a{color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none}
.article-body a:hover{text-decoration:underline}
.article-body code{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;background:var(--surface-2);padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:var(--accent-hover)}
.fact-box{background:var(--accent-light);border-left:3px solid var(--accent);border-radius:0 var(--radius) var(--radius) 0;padding:14px 18px;margin:0 0 20px}
.fact-box p{margin:0;font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.7}
.fact-box strong{color:var(--ink)}
.pc{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin:18px 0}
.pros{background:#f0fdf4;border:1px solid #86efac;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:16px 18px}
.cons{background:#fef2f2;border:1px solid #fca5a5;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:16px 18px}
.pros h4{font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#15803d;margin-bottom:8px}
.cons h4{font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#b91c1c;margin-bottom:8px}
.pros li,.cons li{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:5px}
.use-box{background:var(--surface-2);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:14px 18px;margin:14px 0}
.use-box h4{font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:8px}
/* Comments */
.comments-section{border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:24px 32px;background:var(--surface-2)}
.comments-header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:16px}
.comments-header h4{font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink)}
.c-count{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-muted);background:white;border:1px solid var(--border);padding:2px 10px;border-radius:20px}
.empty-c{text-align:center;padding:24px 16px;background:white;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);margin-bottom:16px}
.empty-c .ei{font-size:28px;margin-bottom:8px}
.empty-c h5{font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:4px}
.empty-c p{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-muted);margin:0}
.comment{display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:16px}
.c-av{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;font-size:12px;color:white;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif}
.c-bubble{flex:1;background:white;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:10px 14px}
.c-meta{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:5px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.c-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink)}
.c-role{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-muted);background:var(--surface-2);padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px}
.c-time{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-muted);margin-left:auto}
.c-text{font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.6}
.c-actions{display:flex;gap:10px;margin-top:6px}
.c-btn{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-muted);background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;padding:2px 0;transition:color .15s}
.c-btn:hover{color:var(--accent)}
.c-gate{background:white;border:1.5px dashed var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px;text-align:center}
.c-gate h4{font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px}
.c-gate p{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:14px}
.c-gate .btns{display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.c-form{display:none;margin-top:14px}
.c-form.active{display:block}
.c-form textarea{width:100%;padding:10px 14px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;font-size:14px;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;color:var(--ink);resize:vertical;min-height:76px;margin-bottom:8px;transition:border-color .2s;outline:none;background:white}
.c-form textarea:focus{border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(249,115,22,.1)}
.c-form-footer{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
.c-char{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-muted)}
.btn-post{padding:8px 20px;background:var(--accent);color:white;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;border:none;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}
.btn-post:hover{background:var(--accent-hover);transform:translateY(-1px)}
/* Sidebar */
.news-sidebar{position:sticky;top:88px}
.sb-card{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:20px}
.sb-head{padding:16px 18px;background:var(--surface-2);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.sb-head h3{font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink)}
.sb-head p{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-muted);margin-top:2px}
.sb-body{padding:10px 14px;background:white}
.proto-row{display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;padding:9px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s}
.proto-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.proto-row:hover .pr-title{color:var(--accent)}
.pr-icon{width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:7px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:15px;flex-shrink:0}
.pr-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:1px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.pr-sub{font-size:10px;color:var(--ink-muted)}
.s-live{color:#16a34a}
.s-beta{color:#d97706}
.s-rc{color:#9333ea}
.nl-card{background:var(--accent-light);border:1px solid var(--accent-border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:20px;margin-bottom:20px}
.nl-card h3{font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:6px}
.nl-card p{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:14px;line-height:1.6}
.nl-input{width:100%;padding:9px 12px;border-radius:7px;border:none;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:8px;outline:none}
.btn-nl{width:100%;padding:9px;background:var(--accent);color:white;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;border:none;border-radius:7px;cursor:pointer;transition:background .2s}
.btn-nl:hover{background:var(--accent-hover)}
.tl-card{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);overflow:hidden}
.tl-item{display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);align-items:flex-start}
.tl-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.tl-dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:5px}
.tl-date{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:1px}
.tl-text{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.4}
/* Modal */
.modal-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(10,14,26,.7);z-index:1000;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:24px;backdrop-filter:blur(4px);opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity .25s}
.modal-overlay.active{opacity:1;pointer-events:all}
.modal-box{background:white;border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:48px;max-width:440px;width:100%;box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);transform:translateY(20px);transition:transform .25s;position:relative}
.modal-overlay.active .modal-box{transform:translateY(0)}
.modal-close{position:absolute;top:16px;right:18px;background:none;border:none;font-size:24px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--ink-muted)}
.modal-box h2{font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:6px}
.modal-box p{font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:20px;line-height:1.7}
.modal-box input{width:100%;padding:10px 14px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;font-size:14px;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;margin-bottom:10px;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s}
.modal-box input:focus{border-color:var(--accent)}
.btn-ms{width:100%;padding:13px;background:var(--accent);color:white;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;border:none;border-radius:9px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}
.btn-ms:hover{background:var(--accent-hover)}
footer{background:#18181B;color:#71717A;border-top:1px solid #27272A;padding:36px 32px;text-align:center}
footer p{font-size:13px}
footer a{color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none;margin:0 8px}
/* Share buttons */
.share-btns{display:flex;gap:6px;margin-left:auto}
.share-btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;transition:all .15s;border:1px solid var(--border)}
.share-btn:hover{transform:translateY(-1px)}
.share-btn-li{color:#0A66C2;background:#f0f7ff}.share-btn-li:hover{background:#0A66C2;color:white;border-color:#0A66C2}
.share-btn-x{color:#18181B;background:var(--surface-2)}.share-btn-x:hover{background:#18181B;color:white;border-color:#18181B}
.share-btn svg{width:14px;height:14px;fill:currentColor}
/* Industry feed */
.industry-divider{padding:32px 0 20px;border-top:2px solid var(--border);margin-top:32px}
.industry-divider h2{font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-weight:400;font-size:28px;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:4px}
.industry-divider p{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-muted)}
.ext-card{display:block;background:var(--surface-card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:18px 22px;margin-bottom:12px;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;transition:all .15s}
.ext-card:hover{border-color:var(--accent-border);box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(249,115,22,.05);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.ext-meta{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.ext-source{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:20px;background:var(--surface-2)}
.ext-date{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-muted);margin-left:auto}
.ext-title{font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.35;margin-bottom:6px}
.ext-summary{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:10px}
.ext-foot{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
.ext-readmore{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--accent)}
.ext-card:hover .ext-readmore{text-decoration:underline}
#feed-loader{text-align:center;padding:24px;color:var(--ink-muted);font-size:13px}
@media(max-width:900px){.news-layout{grid-template-columns:1fr}.news-sidebar{position:static}.pc{grid-template-columns:1fr}.nav-links{display:none}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="modal-overlay" id="signupModal">
  <div class="modal-box">
    <button class="modal-close" onclick="closeModal()">×</button>
    <div style="font-size:28px;margin-bottom:12px">🐙</div>
    <h2>Join the community</h2>
    <p>Create a free Pievra account to post comments, follow protocol updates, and connect with the programmatic AI community.</p>
    <input type="email" id="mEmail" placeholder="Work email"/>
    <input type="text" id="mName" placeholder="Your name"/>
    <button class="btn-ms" onclick="submitSignup()">Create free account →</button>
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-muted);text-align:center;margin-top:10px">Already registered? <a href="#" style="color:var(--accent)" onclick="doLogin()">Sign in</a></p>
  </div>
</div>

<nav>
  <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
    <span style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:24px;color:#18181B">pievra<span style="color:#F97316">.</span></span>
  </a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/marketplace">Marketplace</a>
    <a href="/partners">Partners</a>
    <a href="/news">News</a>
    <a href="/careers">Careers</a>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-right">
    <a href="/signin" style="color:#71717A;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:8px;transition:all .2s">Sign In</a>
    <a href="/signup" style="background:#F97316;color:white;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;padding:8px 18px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;transition:all .2s">Sign Up Free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="news-hero">
  <div class="section-tag">Protocol Intelligence</div>
  <h1>The Pievra<br/>Protocol Briefing</h1>
  <p>In-depth analysis of the five AI agent protocols reshaping programmatic advertising in 2025–2026. Real launch dates. Verified facts. No invented commentary.</p>
  <div class="news-filters">
    <button class="nf active" onclick="filterArticles(this,'all')">All</button>
    <button class="nf" onclick="filterArticles(this,'adcp')">AdCP</button>
    <button class="nf" onclick="filterArticles(this,'mcp')">MCP</button>
    <button class="nf" onclick="filterArticles(this,'ucp')">Agentic Audiences/UCP</button>
    <button class="nf" onclick="filterArticles(this,'artf')">ARTF</button>
    <button class="nf" onclick="filterArticles(this,'a2a')">A2A</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="news-layout">
<main>

<!-- AdCP -->
<article class="article-card" data-proto="adcp">
  <div class="article-header">
    <div class="meta-row">
      <span class="pb pb-adcp">AdCP</span>
      <span class="art-date">15 October 2025</span>
      <span class="art-date">· 9 min read</span>
      <div class="share-btns">
        <a class="share-btn share-btn-li" href="https://www.linkedin.com/sharing/share-offsite/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpievra.com%2Fnews%23adcp" target="_blank" title="Share on LinkedIn"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg></a>
        <a class="share-btn share-btn-x" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpievra.com%2Fnews%23adcp&text=Ad%20Context%20Protocol%20(AdCP)%20-%20deep%20dive%20on%20Pievra" target="_blank" title="Share on X"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/></svg></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h2 class="article-title">Ad Context Protocol (AdCP) - The Open Standard Built on MCP That Launched Agentic Advertising</h2>
    <p class="article-excerpt">On 15 October 2025, a consortium of 20+ companies led by Yahoo, PubMatic, Optable, Scope3, Swivel, and Triton Digital publicly launched AdCP - the first open standard enabling AI agents to execute advertising tasks across any platform. GitHub first release: v2.0.0. Current production version: v2.5. v3.0 RC2 in active development.</p>
    <p class="source-line">Sources: <a href="https://adcontextprotocol.org" target="_blank">adcontextprotocol.org</a> · <a href="https://docs.adcontextprotocol.org" target="_blank">AdCP docs</a> · <a href="https://digiday.com/media-buying/wtf-ad-context-protocol/" target="_blank">Digiday</a> · <a href="https://shellypalmer.com/2025/10/adcp-ad-context-protocol-a-real-attempt-to-make-agents-buy-media/" target="_blank">Shelly Palmer</a> · <a href="https://www.adweek.com/media/adcp-ad-context-protocol-agentic-advertising-standard/" target="_blank">Adweek</a></p>
    <button class="expand-btn" onclick="toggleArticle(this,'adcp-body')">Read full analysis <span class="arr">›</span></button>
  </div>
  <div class="article-body" id="adcp-body">
    <div class="fact-box"><p><strong>Verified facts:</strong> Launched 15 Oct 2025 · GitHub first release v2.0.0 · Production v2.5 · v3.0-rc.2 in development (not for production) · Steward: AgenticAdvertising.org - Delaware 501(c)(6) non-profit incorporated 2025 · Built on MCP and A2A as transport layers · Prebid.org managing open-source Seller Agents project · 20+ founding members: Yahoo, PubMatic, Optable, Scope3, Swivel, Triton Digital, Magnite, Kargo, LG Ad Solutions, Raptive, The Weather Company, Samba TV, Butler/Till, Classify, Newton Research, AccuWeather and others</p></div>

    <h3>What AdCP Is</h3>
    <p>AdCP is an open technical standard that enables AI agents to communicate with advertising platforms through a unified interface - and, as it evolves, directly with each other. It is the agentic successor to OpenRTB: where OpenRTB standardised real-time bidding transactions, AdCP standardises agentic advertising workflows across the entire campaign lifecycle.</p>
    <p>AdCP is built <em>on top of</em> Anthropic's MCP and Google's A2A as its transport layers. It defines domain-specific advertising tasks and schemas that run over these general-purpose agent communication protocols. MCP and A2A are the infrastructure; AdCP defines the advertising vocabulary and rules running over that infrastructure.</p>

    <h3>The Four Protocol Domains (v2.5 - current production)</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Signals Activation Protocol:</strong> Agents discover and activate audience signals - identity, contextual, geographic, temporal - across connected platforms using natural language queries.</li>
      <li><strong>Media Buy Protocol:</strong> Standardises how agents execute and optimise media purchases across all compatible platforms from one interface.</li>
      <li><strong>Creative Protocol:</strong> Enables agents to build, optimise, and deploy creative assets. AI-generated creative integrates into the workflow.</li>
      <li><strong>Curation Protocol:</strong> Marked "Coming Q2 2025" at launch; in active development in v3.0. Allows inventory curation with activated signals.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works in Practice</h3>
    <p>A buyer's AI assistant receives a natural language brief: "Reach eco-conscious car buyers on CTV in the US this week, $10K budget." The agent translates this into structured AdCP requests, queries compatible Seller Agents via MCP or A2A, receives standardised responses, and executes the buy - without custom integrations per platform. Prebid's stewardship of the Seller Agents project is the mechanism ensuring broad publisher adoption without fragmentation.</p>
    <p>AdCP's governance layer adds <code>check_governance</code> validation - verifying budget limits, brand safety, and compliance before any campaign launches, with a complete audit trail of every agent decision.</p>

    <div class="use-box"><h4>🎯 Primary use cases</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Natural language campaign planning across all connected platforms simultaneously</li>
      <li>Direct agent-to-agent inventory negotiation without exchange intermediaries</li>
      <li>Cross-platform audience activation from a single campaign brief</li>
      <li>SMB access to programmatic - no dedicated technical team required</li>
      <li>Supply path optimisation with transparent deal economics</li>
    </ul></div>

    <div class="pc">
      <div class="pros"><h4>✓ Upsides</h4><ul>
        <li>First mover - 20+ founding members at launch</li>
        <li>Built on proven MCP + A2A transports</li>
        <li>Prebid managing Seller Agents - credible adoption path</li>
        <li>Natural language interface lowers barrier to entry</li>
        <li>Non-profit governance - no single vendor control</li>
        <li>v3.0 RC2 already in development - active roadmap</li>
      </ul></div>
      <div class="cons"><h4>✗ Downsides</h4><ul>
        <li>IAB Tech Lab's Katsur publicly sceptical - protocol fragmentation risk</li>
        <li>Only launched Oct 2025 - no at-scale production track record</li>
        <li>Security infrastructure nascent (no SECURITY.md at v2.0 launch)</li>
        <li>Curation Protocol still in development</li>
        <li>Governance non-profit still being formally incorporated</li>
        <li>Tension with IAB Tech Lab's parallel AAMP initiative</li>
      </ul></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="comments-section">
    <div class="comments-header"><h4>Community Discussion</h4><span class="c-count" id="cnt-adcp">0 comments</span></div>
    <div id="list-adcp">
